{
  "stem": "2533.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they got together, and they-- they started to-- to organize it and work it out, where and what and-- Feldhendler, Leon Feldhendler.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the one who started before the Russian came to think about-- if we are going to escape, they said, it has to be all or not at all.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you knew him and listened to him speaking?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not allowed to listen speaking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything was such in secret, that even when they were speaking amongst each other, one day they had, I think a-- they were playing chess or something, or similar to chess, and that's why [INAUDIBLE] they converted amongst themselves with Pechersky because they needed somebody who could speak Russian.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they managed somehow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But before that, that was in the third camp, because nobody who ever went near the third camp did not come back alive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And while I was sorting, an electrician came to fix up the lights in the barracks where we were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he handed me a note.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was from my brother, that he was in a third camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a certain day when he will come to get the lorry, because the food for the third camp was in such like a little wagon on rails, and that was pushed to the gates.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people from the other side opened the gate and took the food in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then later on, they pushed the empty back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a particular time, he will be collecting the-- that-- that wagon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If I could just carry a bundle to that window, already a packed-up bundle of clothes to that window, I'll be able to see him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I did see him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I didn't recognize him.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
